Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:03.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}阿扎提斯坦王國  首都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分軍事政變已經被鎮壓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但城市裡仍然存在恐怖襲擊的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請諸位國民不要出門  留在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿扎提斯坦第一公主  瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位  請保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神所賜予的契約之土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民之間的自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對不能允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為改革派帶來了聯合國才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下  請賜予神的囑佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:55.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}阿扎提斯坦王國  王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然不清楚瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪的行蹤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和聯合軍進行聯合搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎仍然還需要一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是最糟糕的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收天線被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的技術員也撤離了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連Celestial Being也介入進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解決現狀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有保護好瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿扎提斯坦王國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以宗教領導人瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪被綁架為導火線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發了內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於這次內亂發展到了政變的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being也使用Gundam進行了武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰術預報員皇·李·諾瑞加不在的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮和洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能阻止阿扎提斯坦王國的內亂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三勢力？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了接受阿扎提斯坦邀請的聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及進行武力介入的我們以外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個誘發內戰的勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個勢力綁架了瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是我的推測而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但吠陀也暗示了相同的意見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測的根據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收天線的建設現場  受到了遠方的導彈攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就火力方面而言  使用了MS的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能運用MS的組織…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓刹那去調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個國家  我們太過於顯眼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據洛克恩的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎應該是這一帶發射的導彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘留反應  這裡確實有MS出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但會是哪裡來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和回收了的登陸艙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種反應  果然錯不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也在對這裡進行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC Trust那邊的意見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞紛爭地區發現的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊偷聽可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是附近的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…聽說這附近發生了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是不理解你到了對這些事感興趣的年齡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這附近仍然很危險  你最好快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  馬上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看待這個國家的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:05:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼看待這個國家的內亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法作出客觀的判斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你支持哪方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…都不支持
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺兩邊都有著自己的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為這次戰鬥  有人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了很多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為軍人的你也是這麼想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這個國家的我們很礙事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  如果來了很多的軍人的話  受害也會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面藏著的是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  昨天從這裡攻擊接收天線的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是AEU最新銳的Enact吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那部機體似乎是從莫拉里亞的PMC搶的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆  為什麼說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴也沒什麼藉口的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC的Enact…難道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…那個男人…和這次內亂有關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何…為何到現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是恐怖襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這附近改革派很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用MS應對沒什麼效果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能要求派遣對人鎮壓用自動機器人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是專為Gundam派來的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高層不可能派更多的部隊來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會精打細算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受神的懲罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪…瑪麗娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜予神的囑佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太沒用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改革派的爪牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要如此相互憎恨呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,POINT F3987？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比沒有強…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帶紅龍一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對救出重要人物會有幫助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN系統保險解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先權轉至刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部迷彩解凍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持散佈GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入登機模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  開始執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎  紅龍先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  前往目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老頭別說吃飯了  連水都不喝一滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想接受敵人的施捨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這個國家的傢伙都很頑固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial什麼的一來  全都搞得亂糟糟的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  有朝這裡接近的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合的偵查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那白色的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam由我來應付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上老頭撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Enact
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  駕駛員果然是那個克魯吉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼知道這個隱蔽地點的話一點都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到啊  那個時候的小鬼會坐上了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰鬥還沒結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯已經滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的神到底在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要回答你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了  那台機體讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真做得出來啊  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然在預料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未必吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  我們遭到敵人襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個人交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手看來還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對阿扎提斯坦的內戰進行武力干涉的私立武裝組織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  就是你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的任務  確實已經收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼作戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的下達了那樣的指示嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一步錯了  Exia就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最切實的辦法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成皇小姐的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有讓世界見識的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下  Celestial Being發來了訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being發來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「已救出瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪  正在前來」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「並希望公主立刻召開停戰會議  以上」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  馬上去做會談的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實我不贊同他們的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  即使如此也很想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想相信他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being正在前往王宮  是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還帶著人質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣的話可是最好的機會啊  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拭目以待吧  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是阿扎提斯坦的王宮前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪已被救出並正在前往王宮的市民們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紛紛聚集到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是未經證實的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有消息說救出拉弗瑪迪的是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  Gundam會在這裡出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  作為改革派的象徵——瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能實現和保守派的宗教領導人的雙邊會談的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦的內亂很有可能將會終結
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把沙慈放開啊  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam從高空降落下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛  Gundam在王宮前緩緩著陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然解除了武裝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢啊  居然毫無武裝的來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要攻擊Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出這片契約之地！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是槍擊  數名市民正在向Gundam射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝著王宮慢慢前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即釋放挾持的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複  立即釋放挾持的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請前往王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不算是很舒適的一趟旅程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該向你道謝才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being保護瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪並移送到了王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  真的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來全看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是否還會再來也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧  為了你所信奉的神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉  追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話Gundam還…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的話  我們將會成為世界的靶子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇出了一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣這個問題就能解決了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能為阻止人們的紛爭走出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪宣佈綁架他的武裝集團是傭兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及此次內亂是精心籌劃的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主謀似乎是企圖阻止阿扎提斯坦的近代化變革的勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有發表任何犯罪聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後  瑪麗娜·伊斯邁爾及瑪斯德·拉弗瑪迪發佈共同聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼籲國民停止內戰及恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:22:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  阿扎提斯坦的內亂至今仍在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:16.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}絶望は甘い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}鎖されたその扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:30.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心が戦場だから誰にも救えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:40.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}ゼンマイの心臓が運命に操られ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:50.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}ブリキの兵隊達は殺戮を始める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.69,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}愛を知らず揺れるゆりかご
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}燃え尽きてく眠りの森で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:05.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}共に生きる喜びさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:10.76,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}消えてしまう　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:16.51,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}優しさを信じ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:21.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}全てを許して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:25.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}慈しむように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:32.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}ただわかちあって　わかりあって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.82,0:22:16.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}絕望是甜蜜的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那扇門被緊緊地鎖著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:30.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心靈即為戰場　誰都無法得到救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:40.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心臟如線牽的木偶　被命運操縱著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:50.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}身著鍍錫鐵皮的士兵們　開始了殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:55.69,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}不懂愛為何物　便搖晃的搖籃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}將要在沉睡的森林中燃燒殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:05.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就連共同倖存下來的喜悅心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:10.76,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}也消失在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:16.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}堅信你的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:21.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}原諒你的所有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:25.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同憐愛之情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:32.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}只是　互相分享　互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由三個國家群的共同軍事演習引起的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著奔向險境的Meister心中襲來的東西會是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「決意的早晨」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Gundam的話…


